=== Template Fluids Simulation ===

-- Compiling the code --

This code works on Linux et MacOSX. A few modifications are necessary for Windows.
It needs :
 OpenGL3 
 libSDL

* First, compile TinyXML
 cd ./api/TinyXML
 make
 ar rcs libtinyxml.a tinyxmlerror.o tinystr.o tinyxmlparser.o tinyxml.o

* Compile Fluids :
 cd ./src
 make


-- Running the simulation

* Run Fluids
 cd ./src
 ./Fluids

